<p>Welcome to Papa's Pizzeria! Where every pizza is handmade to order! Our homemade pizza crust is made fresh daily. These classic and specialty Russo's Pizza originals blend your favorite ingredients to create distinctive and memorable flavor combination. Russo's Pizza has been known for their specialty pizza, but their traditional pizzas are also a fan favorite as well. Try our amazing specialty pizza's either personal, medium, or family size!</p>

<h2>AWARDS</h2>
<p>over the past several decades, Russo's Pizzaria has won a multitude of awards from the greater Columnus area. Below are awards Russo's has one in the past cuople of years</p>
<ul>
<li>Ohio Best Pizzaeria, 2018</li>
<li>National Small Business Awards,2019</li>
<li>Small Business Influencer Awards,2018</li>
<li>Indie Awards, 2017</li>
<li>Best in Biz Awards,2018</li>
