<h2>HISTORY</h2>
<p>In, 1932, Guieppe Russo and his younger sister, Aurora started the family business. the both had a passion for cooking and using family recipes to enlighten their guest for various occasions. After multiple years of cooking for friends and family, Guiseppe and Aurora decided to open their own business rignt in the heart of Columbus, Ohio. Guiseppe and Aurora hope to share their joy and happiness of cooking with the rest of their community.</p>

<h2>TODAY</h2>
<p>Almost 90 years later, Guiseppe and Aurora no longer run Russo's Pisseria, but there two Grandsons do. Simone and Paola Russo keeps the family memories alive by creating homemode specialty pizzas with the same, old-fashion, family recipes. Simon and Paolo have taken the traditional pizza that the community has coe to love and updated it with specialty pizza ideas. Simon and Paolo have taken comon and unique foods and turn then into various types of pizza. With a little twist on the traditional pizza. Russo's Pizza has made it on the top of Columbus community as the top Speciaalty Pizzeria in the area.</p>



